PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for the purposes of the Atlantic Canada Opportunities Agency Act of Barry Martin, of Sydney, Nova Scotia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Enterprise Cape Breton Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years, in the place of Gordon Macaulay, Sr., whose term has expired.
